	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />To give a code sample, I'd need to know how your game loop is structured. Are you running everything in the NMI handler, everything in the main thread, or a mix of the two?
<br />
<br />To set the scroll position, do this as the last thing in the vertical blanking handler:
<br /><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">&nbsp; lda elapsed_nmis&nbsp; ; using this as the horizontal value<br />&nbsp; sta $2005<br />&nbsp; lda #0&nbsp; ; using this as the vertical value<br />&nbsp; sta $2005<br /></div>

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


